      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues] Line 65: `showOriginal` is delegate-local mutable state, but QML list delegates are commonly reused. After a user toggles one overwritten message, the recycled delegate can display another message in the wrong mode. Reset this state when the represented message changes.\n\n```suggestion\nproperty bool showOriginal: false\n\nonIdChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\nonBodyChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\nonOriginalBodyChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\n```",
