      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues] Line 80: Returning `OriginalBody` directly bypasses the existing `MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(...)` path used for normal message bodies. That can produce inconsistent rendering for links/emoji/previews and may also bypass whatever escaping/sanitization `ParsedBody` normally provides before assigning text to the delegate. Please parse/render the original body through the same pipeline as `Body`, or add a separate parsed-original role/cache before displaying it.\n\n```suggestion\nif (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite) {\n    MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(Id, OriginalBody, UtilsAdapter.getAppValue(Settings.DisplayHyperlinkPreviews), rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n    return \"\";\n}\n```",
